text: From Me to You is the second album by American rapper Crunchy Black. Released on June 12, 2007, the album contains 16 tracks and was rated as one of the best albums of the year in 2007. The album peaked at number ten on the Billboard Top Rap Albums chart. == Track listing == == References == ==External links== *[ Billboard.com] Category:2007 albums Category:Crunchy Black albums
